{"tid":1456962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不流血、不被捕","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:04:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:10:02.000Z","uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6def8dba04ae92edadde48e6fb26886ebe99af1","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:04:44.000Z","msg":"第一次開po，係因為見到連登巴絲竟然因為要唔要留守機場而喺到嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n去到今時今日場運動仲可以繼續都係因為大家相信「不割蓆、不分化」、「兄弟爬山、各自努力」、「Be Water」等等，點解大家會為左去留機場而嘈？<br />\n<br />\n721、811既事，每位真．香港人見到都係嬲到爆，但唔好意氣用事！依場運動係持久戰，真係少一個戰友就少一份力。所以不論勇武定係和理，總之喺前線既都要記得好好保護自己同戰友。做到「不流血、不被捕」就係每次決定留守定散水既準則！<br />\n<br />\n香港人assemble!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10dafeb318da20cc41138f12dffeebef4641708f","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:05:29.000Z","msg":"而行唔行出街既決定，取決於政府幾時回應五大訴求！"},{"pid":"527bf24e52dd4016378f5941b894a324e3c3608e","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:05:51.000Z","msg":"香港人Be Water! Be safe!"},{"pid":"a221c339aacfa3ed441c732c0f53402efb40e75b","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:08:38.000Z","msg":"係唔係都要自推十式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef11fccae452c8089955749558fdc81e743c68c","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dc68a8624db50e4897ec43589b96bcf48dee8a1","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:09:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0be9e005bd69165e840e2644eccb01be2bb582","tid":1456962,"uid":227280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim